    nursingActions: ["Teach blood glucose self-monitoring technique", "Educate on dietary modifications (carbohydrate counting, portion control)", "Monitor for signs of hypoglycemia and hyperglycemia", "Assess fetal movement patterns (kick counts)", "Monitor for signs of complications (preeclampsia, macrosomia, polyhydramnios)", "Educate on importance of postpartum glucose screening (6-12 weeks)", "Report blood glucose consistently above target to provider"],
